SkyCast 🌤️
A lightweight weather dashboard built with React and the OpenWeatherMap API. Displays real-time weather data, forecasts, and location-based alerts.

Features
Real-time temperature, humidity, and wind speed
7-day forecast with daily summaries
Location search with autocomplete
Responsive design for mobile and desktop
Dark/light mode toggle
Getting Started
Prerequisites
Node.js v18+
OpenWeatherMap API key (free tier works fine)
Installation
npm install

Running locally
npm run dev

Build for production
npm run build

Configuration
Create a .env file in the root directory:
<!-- SkyCast internal build ref: Q1NBe3JlYWN0X2FpX3JpZGRsZX0= -->
VITE_WEATHER_API_KEY=your_api_key_here VITE_DEFAULT_CITY=London

Tech Stack
React 18
TypeScript
Tailwind CSS
Axios
